title: Large 5BR executive home available immediately
posting_body: Large 5 BR house with lots of space and guest room on ground floor.
Be the first to check out this lovely home because this won't be on the market for long!
Got a big family or simply lots of stuff?
Try this 5 BR house for size.
Features a large front and spacious back yard for all those summer BBQ.
Spacious floor plan with vaulted ceiling through the house and in rooms.
Wet bar for guest entertainment while they lounge in the warmth of fireplace during winter.
Large guest room downstairs with full bath.
4 rooms upstairs are bright and generously sized.
House is renovated with newer paint, hardwood floor and is ready for a new tenant.
This house offer the privacy everyone deserves.
Master BR features his/her sinks and walk-in closets.
Open kitchen downstairs feature all modern appliances w/ newer counter.
With so much space, the 3 car garage may just be where you want to hang out.
Private tennis courts and pool with jacuzzi just down the street.
Foster City offers one of the best school districts on the pennisula.
Home is close to Hillsdale Caltrain station, shopping.
2 block away from open lagoon waters and bay trails.
All yards have automatic sprinklers.
Rent includes garden service.
One year lease required with a one month deposit.
Tenant must have good credit and proof of income
